          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-7042 ofed: Handle OFED 3.18 packaging definitions",
        "message": "LU-7042 ofed: Handle OFED 3.18 packaging definitions\n\nStarting with OFED 3.18 the OFED package started to use\nAC_PACKAGE_NAME macro which is also used by Lustre. This\nlead to clash between the two in the ko2iblnd driver.\nThe solution is to undefine the PACKAGE_XXX values set\nin compact-2.6.h so the proper lustre PACKAGE_XXX values\nare used.\n\nChange-Id: I64ea2709600165a01c2f1d086fceeca6778ae53f\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@yahoo.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
